Introduction

TIOT, short for TIME IS OUR TURN, is a five-member boy group under Redstart ENM. They debuted on April 22, 2024, with the mini album Kick-Start.

On August 1st, it was announced that REDSTART BOYS changed their name to TIOT. They released their pre-debut mini album titled "Frame the Blueprint: Prelude to Possibilities" on August 23.
